    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone willing to put in a little work. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car shows its age with some noticeable exterior scratches, a few small dings, and interior wear on the upholstery. While it remains reliable for daily commuting, it may soon require routine maintenance items like new tires and a brake service. It is a dependable driver that offers good value for someone looking for functional transportation without the premium price of a newer or better-maintained model.",
