      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence, maintained to a standard rarely seen outside a private collection. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish with no swirl marks or stone chips, and a cabin that still retains its new-car scent. Every surface, from the hand-stitched leather upholstery to the polished interior accents, is completely free of wear or blemishes. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, having been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships with a full, documented history. Equipped with every premium option and riding on immaculate wheels with deep tire treads, this car drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. For the discerning buyer who demands perfection, this is a turnkey opportunity to own a masterfully preserved machine.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
